ion took such a steamy turn on the show that Bush Hager admitted she was beginning to feel \\\"uncomfortable.\\\"  \\\"You do not need to do it in a store because you have your own bedroom!\\\" Bush Hager said after Kotb's shocking confession.  \\\"It's not about needing!\\\" Kotb fired back. She later added, \\\"It was totally sexy. And a turn on, yes.\\\"  Bush Hager even tried toset Kotb up with Dave Bautistawhen he visitedTodayto promoteMy Spy: The Eternal City. After finding out he's single, Bush Hager told her co-host, \\\"Hoda, get closer to Dave! Dave is handsome. You look great, Dave. We can see it.\\\"  Today with Hoda & Jennaairs on weekdays at 10/9c on NBC.  This story has been shared 1,178 times.1,178  This story has been shared 513 times.513  This story has been shared 446 times.446  This story has been shared 421 times.421  This story has been shared 408 times.408  This story has been shared 270 times.270  This story has been shared 264 times.264  This story has been shared 262 times.262  This story has been shared 214 times.214  This story has been shared 213 times.213  This story has been shared 187 times.187  This story has been shared 167 times.167  This story has been shared 162 times.162  This story has been shared 159 times.159  This story has been shared 134 times.134\"}"